# GPIO Mapping

| Component | ESP32 Pin | Notes |
|-----------|-----------|-------|
| Capacitive Soil Moisture Sensor | GPIO34 | Analog Input (ADC) |
| DS18B20 Waterproof Temperature Sensor | GPIO4 | OneWire |
| DHT22 Temperature & Humidity Sensor | GPIO15 | Digital Data |
| OLED Display SDA | GPIO21 | I²C Data |
| OLED Display SCL | GPIO22 | I²C Clock |

## Power

All modules operate at **3.3V**.

All GND pins are connected to the common ground rail.

The DS18B20 data line uses a **4.7kΩ pull-up resistor** connected between DQ and 3.3V.
